%% Diagram: Device Authorization Grant (RFC 8628)
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant Device as Device (TV / CLI)
    participant AuthZ as Authorization Server
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant User

    Device->>AuthZ: POST /device_authorization<br/>client_id, scope
    AuthZ->>Device: device_code, user_code,<br/>verification_uri[_complete],<br/>expires_in, interval
    Device->>User: Display user_code + verification_uri<br/>(or QR for verification_uri_complete)

    par User-side approval
        User->>Browser: Open verification_uri,<br/>enter user_code
        Browser->>AuthZ: Authenticate + consent
    and Device polling
        loop Until approved / expired
            Device->>AuthZ: POST /token<br/>grant_type=urn:ietf:params:oauth:grant-type:device_code<br/>device_code, client_id
            AuthZ-->>Device: 400 authorization_pending<br/>or slow_down (back off +5s)
        end
    end

    AuthZ->>Device: access_token, refresh_token,<br/>(id_token if openid scope)
